02:56.802 --> 03:01.181
But I just felt like
I was used an example

03:01.181 --> 03:03.350
all of a sudden. Done.

03:03.350 --> 03:06.895
Districts have become
over reactionary

03:06.895 --> 03:10.399
and the fact
