03:10.399 --> 03:11.942
is kind of painful.

03:11.942 --> 03:18.240
For me, grooming
is a willful intention

03:18.240 --> 03:23.203
to drag the student into
a more intimate relationship.

03:23.203 --> 03:25.747
You know, "Can I see you?"

03:25.747 --> 03:27.624
It could be sending an image.

03:27.624 --> 03:30.252
It could be, you know,
an inappropriate text,

03:30.252 --> 03:33.463
if you try to instigate
private meetings,

03:33.463 --> 03:36.550
"Send me a picture of you,"

03:36.550 --> 03:38.385
"Oh, my God, that looks hot,"

03:38.385 --> 03:40.720
wanting to talk off-hours--

03:40.720 --> 03:42.597
that kind of stuff.

03:42.597 --> 03:43.974
To me,
that would be an instance

03:43.974 --> 03:46.268
of definite grooming.

03:46.268 --> 03:50.397
♪ ♪

