06:21.756 --> 06:23.341
You know, she's often described
as, you know,

06:23.341 --> 06:25.468
like a ray of sunshine
and I feel like

06:25.468 --> 06:27.178
that is the true Heaven.

06:27.178 --> 06:30.098
At her core she is just
so sweet and loving.

06:30.098 --> 06:33.810
But then no one sees
the hours she spends in bed

06:33.810 --> 06:36.062
just, like, crying
because there is so much--

06:36.062 --> 06:38.315
or she feels like everything
is on her

06:38.315 --> 06:39.900
and she is constantly
double-checking

06:39.900 --> 06:42.360
and second-guessing
every move that she makes.

06:42.360 --> 06:45.405
She doesn't expect
to be believed.

06:45.405 --> 06:48.450
She comes prepared
with every single thing

06:48.450 --> 06:52.621
I need to explain to make sure
