06:52.621 --> 06:54.289
because that is what everyone
else showed her

06:54.289 --> 06:55.790
she needed to do.

06:55.790 --> 06:57.459
It feels like
it would be chaos

06:57.459 --> 06:59.628
to be in Heaven's head.

06:59.628 --> 07:04.049
