07:07.761 --> 07:09.929
♪ ♪

07:09.929 --> 07:13.183
The teachers
and the administration

07:13.183 --> 07:16.144
at my high school really made
me feel like it was my fault,

07:16.144 --> 07:18.104
and they played a role

07:18.104 --> 07:21.816
in, like, that psychological,
like--

07:21.816 --> 07:24.152
where you can't trust yourself

07:24.152 --> 07:26.446
because you're like,
