08:47.152 --> 08:48.945
And I was like, "Thanks."

08:48.945 --> 08:51.948
Like, "I like you too.
Like, cool.

08:51.948 --> 08:53.992
This class is awesome."

08:53.992 --> 08:56.786
And he said, "No, I'm serious.
