09:04.210 --> 09:05.879
I just kept going on.

09:05.879 --> 09:07.297
And then
there was another time

09:07.297 --> 09:10.008
where he'd said, you know,

09:10.008 --> 09:12.218
"I don't know
if I've told you this before,

09:12.218 --> 09:14.387
but I struggle with insomnia."

09:14.387 --> 09:15.555
And he said, "And you know,

09:15.555 --> 09:16.806
"when the school year
