09:16.806 --> 09:19.017
"that sometimes can ramp up,

09:19.017 --> 09:20.977
"and I have, like, a problem
with my insomnia,

09:20.977 --> 09:23.563
"but I haven't been feeling
that way

09:23.563 --> 09:26.816
since we started working
together."

09:27.692 --> 09:29.861
- Something about the
admiration in his eyes

09:29.861 --> 09:32.572
as I was childlike
seemed comforting.

09:32.572 --> 09:34.324
Rarely was I rewarded
with kindness

09:34.324 --> 09:36.785
in moments of childlike
behavior.

09:36.785 --> 09:38.870
I remember being conditioned
to grow up

09:38.870 --> 09:41.581
before I knew
what growing up meant.

09:41.581 --> 09:43.041
It made us closer.

09:44.292 --> 09:46.586
He coached me through
some of this pain,

09:46.586 --> 09:48.338
opened portal to poetry

09:48.338 --> 09:52.759
that allowed me to make
friends with pen and page.

09:52.759 --> 09:57.138
I felt he was mentoring me
by sharing common experiences

09:57.138 --> 09:58.848
or giving me advice of, like,

09:58.848 --> 10:00.141
"This won't hurt you
for so long.

10:00.141 --> 10:02.352
"You'll be able to move away
and go to college

10:02.352 --> 10:04.896
"and, like, you'll start
to shape your life and these--

10:04.896 --> 10:06.898
"you know, the stress
