10:11.486 --> 10:16.449
♪ ♪

10:16.449 --> 10:17.742
He said, "Bring me everything
you've written

10:17.742 --> 10:19.285
in the last year."

10:19.285 --> 10:22.747
And a lot of it was, like,
gushy and emotional

10:22.747 --> 10:26.918
and, like, very embarrassing
