10:37.846 --> 10:40.765
to now I'm immature.

10:40.765 --> 10:43.268
So I kind of, like,
put that on myself

10:43.268 --> 10:46.646
of, like, what can I do
to be better?

10:46.646 --> 10:49.190
I had been writing a poem
where I felt like

10:49.190 --> 10:52.068
