13:07.453 --> 13:09.539
who maybe cared about me,

13:09.539 --> 13:12.083
and at that time,
I was certain that he cared.

13:13.167 --> 13:14.961
His cold hands.

13:14.961 --> 13:17.005
The sharpness in his voice.

13:17.005 --> 13:19.674
My isolation.

13:19.674 --> 13:23.219
And during that time,
