13:23.219 --> 13:29.559
Like, way too much
for a 17-year-old to carry.

13:31.769 --> 13:35.815
The anxiety, like,
really started to kick in.

13:35.815 --> 13:38.985
I was having trouble
keeping food down.

13:38.985 --> 13:42.030
I really wasn't eating
very much,

13:42.030 --> 13:44.365
not sleeping very much.

13:44.365 --> 13:48.661
He had told me, you know,
