13:48.661 --> 13:51.539
and so I was pushing
my friends away.

13:51.539 --> 13:56.002
And so this world that I had
worked so hard to create,

13:56.002 --> 13:59.088
where I had had friends

13:59.088 --> 14:02.258
and things I was
interested in doing...

14:02.258 --> 14:04.427
all of those things went away

14:04.427 --> 14:08.056
because of the pressure
and the guilt

14:08.056 --> 14:14.729
and the restrictions
that he made me feel like

14:14.729 --> 14:16.939
would benefit me if I did them.

14:16.939 --> 14:21.069
If--if you don't tell,
then, like...

14:21.069 --> 14:23.071
things are gonna be okay.

14:24.572 --> 14:26.157
And so I just went along.

14:26.157 --> 14:29.243
I tried to follow the rules
as best as I could.

14:32.163 --> 14:34.749
But once he was gone,
after we'd been physical,

14:34.749 --> 14:37.335
