lingering inside of me

14:37.335 --> 14:40.922
and I wanted to itch him
off my skin.

14:40.922 --> 14:43.883
[eerie music]

14:43.883 --> 14:46.928
♪ ♪

14:46.928 --> 14:48.971
- Where can you go?

14:48.971 --> 14:50.723
Those are the people
you're around

14:50.723 --> 14:52.600
eight hours a day.

14:52.600 --> 14:54.894
Everybody condones
this authority

14:54.894 --> 14:56.729
that these men have over you,
