14:56.729 --> 15:00.733
I'm being told by everybody
that these men

15:00.733 --> 15:02.485
who are my teachers

15:02.485 --> 15:04.445
are the ones who are in charge
of me.

15:04.445 --> 15:07.615
That power dynamic, in a way,
is almost ultimate

15:07.615 --> 15:10.201
because everyone around you
is telling you

15:10.201 --> 15:12.161
to trust these people.

15:12.161 --> 15:16.415
I was sort of bred
to be this person.

15:16.415 --> 15:18.459
- So if you took
sort of the culture of Texas

15:18.459 --> 15:22.463
and you sort of concentrated
it down to something,

15:22.463 --> 15:24.423
it was Little Elm. Very small.

15:24.423 --> 15:27.301
I think there were 2,500 people
when I graduated high school

15:27.301 --> 15:31.597
in the town.
