15:31.597 --> 15:35.268
Having your education guided
by white men

15:35.268 --> 15:41.149
and predominantly taught
by white men,

15:41.149 --> 15:44.861
having women's sports teams
run by white men,

15:44.861 --> 15:49.657
definitely gave the impression
and the idea

15:49.657 --> 15:51.534
that white men were superior.

15:51.534 --> 15:55.955
And when you have
a society culture

15:55.955 --> 15:59.375
where white men are
sort of ruling and in charge,

15:59.375 --> 16:01.502
it creates an environment

16:01.502 --> 16:03.337
that's not safe
for anyone else,

16:03.337 --> 16:05.840
certainly not safe for women
and girls,

16:05.840 --> 16:07.758
certainly not safe
for people of color,

16:07.758 --> 16:10.052
certainly not safe
for people who are different.

16:28.571 --> 16:30.156
